data.description: Older home that has been remodeled on the inside from the plumbing to the ceilings. Great size back yard with a huge covered patio area for gatherings. All appliances convey with the property, refrigerator, stove, oven-microwave, dishwasher, food warmer, washer, dryer. Property also has sprinkler system and alarm system.

Quite neighborhood, centrally located in the heart of McAllen near schools, shopping, restaurants, etc. Plenty of room for entertaining guest . View more info at www.417Westway.willsellquick.com Contact seller at 956-266-0939. Realtors are welcome!
